Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.19,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:09.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad that the sports car presentation was a success
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:09.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're working really hard lately, Riko
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You took a loan or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:15.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is your conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is there any other reason than money to work hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's probably....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:21.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Plastic model?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was able to concentrate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:26.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like a brain detox
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:27.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ooishi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hope that you can be just as capable as me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course, my goal is to become the next ace of Department 1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:33.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:36.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Takagi Shinji is gone and the department is not noisy anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji is really dumb, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,His brain is the only thing that seems good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, he's dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you want for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to eat chilled Chinese noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That sounds great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:52.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who was responsible for transferring him to Department 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:54.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors that it was your doing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:55.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:56.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:00:58.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:00:59.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Warm water
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:01.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you being this conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is drinking warm water equals high conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:04.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:10.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe being in Department 1 was too soon for him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:11.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:14.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, good work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.11,0:01:15.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How is Shinji doing in Department 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't push dumb people to Department 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.48,0:01:19.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You got it all wrong, Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:21.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai, you better give Shinji proper guidance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:23.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If there's something that I need to do, then I'll do it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, I leave Shinji in your care, Komukai-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of him too, Nakano-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:28.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:36.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your friend always get on my nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:39.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is Ooishi-san always kind to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:42.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The person who is kind to everyone is usually a psycho, be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you submitted your proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you know, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Walking is better to get oxygen into the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Walk for the rest of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ooishi-san sure is handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of the Interacting with Manten-kun event is Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait just a second
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I absolutely can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows Manten Nodoame better than me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not a good idea to take unnecessary risk
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Someone who understands the inner workings of Department 3 is the most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Above all else, I never had Manten Nodoame before
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you been trained to think of reasons why you can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:15.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say it like that, Saruwatari-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Acting Chief Kijimura, please tell the Chief the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Chief Inuzuka's decision is absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:30.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji-kun, we're busy with planning the biggest event of the year that will take place in a month, Manten-kun's birthday celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This meeting is full with things that can be improved
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is so unproductive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:41.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that Shinji-kun is amazing, being able to decline a project means that he's passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:45.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you support Shinji on this project?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:46.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Saruwatari, go teach Shinji the ropes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do it because I'm swamped with other projects
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you been trained to think of reasons why you can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:53.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll be in your care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This place sure is peaceful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:00.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not like I don't want to be the person in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:08.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The right person in the right place, or rather, I'm good taking the support role and analyzing data
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, you're going to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:21.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:23.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here to support you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're my senior, Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:25.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're the leader, Shinji-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:32.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's start by choosing the venue, because it's a big expenditure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that I missed the normal time to go home....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for not finishing in time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:50.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is the proposal that we came up with is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,First of all, it's great that we even came up with something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to send the data to Saruwatari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no need to send me the data
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you wait for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was just tidying up the place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Show me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:07.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The numbers are all over the place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's our first draft
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:15.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not even good enough to be called that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please be more specific then
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:17.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is now the time to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's way past the normal time to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He ignored me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We have used this venue before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:39.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The venue is close from the train station and attracts a large number of visitors,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,so we expect many families to come to the event
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? I'll leave that to you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:47.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Should we go the shopping district and ask to put up posters for the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We haven't made the script to explain the event to the MC too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As my support, I want you to schedule things for us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's close from here, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're too punctual, Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lunch is decided then
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The budget for the lighting for the venue is way off the mark
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:15.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do we have a place to put it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't mind where you put it on, please put Manten-kun up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She said that Manten-kun will come
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:22.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about over there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:24.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He said it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:25.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm following Manten Nodoame's official account
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mikiki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I love your song "Ganbare Semiko-san"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As I told you before, if you try to fudge up the numbers, it will get found out eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:54.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm taking notes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Click clack click clack
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you're working on something different
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's unforgivable
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:02.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well well welll
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's see it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's dumb, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's motivated, but maybe it's because there's a gap between him and the job
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's Kijimura behind Manten
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:25.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ask me anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Saruwatari-san, does he has a loose screw or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to be a strong drinker, Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't hate alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you had a drink with Saruwatari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no way
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about with Komukai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You should just go and ask them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:41.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a piece of cake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Should I order something expensive to cheer you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:49.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just say to them "Please take me somewhere"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"Please take me somewhere"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's quite a hard thing to say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Should I order some sea urchins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:59.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is Saruwatari-san good at his job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:04.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's only been an hour since we started drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well well
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's the up and coming generation after all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cheers to youth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cheers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you heard something about Shinji from Komukai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not close with that mass production type employee
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Looking at your attitude towards her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that the two of you are childhood friends or something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please don't say such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:28.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The rumor is that Shinji is butting heads with Saruwatari-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're a dry person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:35.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have to be joking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm about to die because it's so out of left field
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The people in Department 1 are more passionate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll do it when the time comes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you working seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:49.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say it because you started it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Stop using your laptop all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want you to step forward even more, because you're the leader after all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was the only one who said something to the client during the meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was also the only one who negotiated putting up the posters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're using your laptop as a shield to avoid risks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Laptop shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like you're not all in on the project
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:09.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was just wrapping my head around it while taking notes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My goal is to analyze those notes later
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I leave Shinji in your care, Komukai-san
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:26.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My goal is to perfectly support you, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:26.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can say anything to me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:33.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:34.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take me somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Somewhere? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Anywhere is fine, as long as it's a place that you often go to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Somewhere that I often to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take me there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What am I looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, we're not going to a bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? So that is what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:05.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you came back for more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:05.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,More?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a large serving this time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A model shop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your boyfriend, Zaku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Zaku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm touched that you brought someone here with you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:20.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's my junior at work, Takagi Shinji-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why plastic models though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You know how it's going to look like in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:28.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They purposely took it apart and then you have to build it yourself, which takes a lot of time and effort, I just can't understand it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Try saying that after you have built one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Try building one, Shinji-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's a waste of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Build this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evangelion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your name is Shinji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm busy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're handsome, Shinji-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have any choice then
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have watched the show before
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, open the box
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The runners are colorful
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can finish building it without using any paint
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, he will teach you all about it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evangelion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone has heard of it before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The gold standard of anime
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:19.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It originally aired in 1995, it became a huge social phenomenon that involves even people who don't watch anime
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It happened before I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was relaunched in 2007 with an all new movie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:27.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The final movie that was released last year was an unprecedented hit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It is truly a masterpiece that will live on in history
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I watched the first and second movies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:36.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the All-Purpose Humanoid Decisive Battle Weapon Artificial Human Evangelion Unit 01
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It is the Eva that the main character, Shinji, uses
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I'm going to do this all on my own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of runners
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:49.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to do this alone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for one person to build it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's going to do it alone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Shinji-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a piece of cake, I have the instruction manual after all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:11:59.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Shinji-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That instruction manual is the coolest thing ever
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You need a lot of patience to complete this plastic model
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, your name is Shinji-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that you should just do it without running away from it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like this is going to take a lot of time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're good at using the nipper
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks a bit rough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is too much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just stop if you feel like it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was just resting my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not a robot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evangelions are man-made humans
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why even the smallest muscles are reproduced
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The large number of parts allows for a high degree of reproducibility
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not a robot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It is alive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have changed my mind about it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The parts that you didn't look at closely doesn't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Being meticulous is important
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to cut it again next time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not good to have a plastic models with gaps within them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You should push it in more
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared! Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It felt like something got inside of me too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:55.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Should I give you a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you saying right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's going to take a while
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the shop
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:03.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please let me do this on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:04.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's proceed, Yassan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:15:59.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go, Shinji-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks so cool
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:26.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The next step is the hands, you can choose from a number of different variations
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:12.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Bare hands, open hands, clenched fists, pallet rifles and even Progressive Knife
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Shinji-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going with clenched fists
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,-Give birth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:24.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I fell asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You look happy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's because I finished it on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You did well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:32.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I saw the view from the front line for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:05.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evangelion is so beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:30.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do our best
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:36.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We used to drink together a lot back in the day, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:52.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You hated it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:56.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all, I was proud that I got to share a drink with the ace of Department 1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What a response
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How is Shinji doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was your doing after all huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:10.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He looks just like me when I first joined the company
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wanted him to learn from you, Saru-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There was an event today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did everything went smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that it was exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, we recorded a loss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was too naive with a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not a surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:30.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The loss was within our expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for covering for his mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Being tasked as a leader for this project
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:39.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I keenly felt that I had not taken a step forward until now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By taking on more responsibility, I was able to see many areas for improvement
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:43.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The first thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:44.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Make it quick
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:46.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Working hard is worth it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:21:59.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to hear from the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's finally at the starting line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was just watching over him this time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Saru-san
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:21.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come back to Department 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:23.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can talk to the higherups
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have that kind of passion anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:26.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:29.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Come here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:35.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare open your laptop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:39.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,